page_title: Azure OpenAI Service API version retirement
page_description: Learn more about API version retirement in Azure OpenAI Services.
chunk_content: Latest GA API releaseAzure OpenAI API version 2024-02-01is currently the latest GA API release. This API version is the replacement for the previous`2023-05-15` GA API release.This version contains support for the latest GA features like Whisper, DALL-E 3, fine-tuning, on your data, etc. Any preview features that were released after the `2023-12-01-preview` release like Assistants, TTS, certain on your data datasources, are only supported in the latest preview API releases.
